{"tid":1480092,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得又有風向撚吹風話聽日好危險，行完要快d散水，仲話聽日勇武嘅就係鬼","createTime":"2019-08-17T07:09:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T07:38:42.000Z","uid":14153,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2e2d590386395fc44f8f904049bfa2e846c91fe5","tid":1480092,"uid":14153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:09:55.000Z","msg":"早幾日已經吹話好多大陸佬落黎搞事，係度白色恐怖，今日就一大堆post話乜都唔帶、最好出去一下就散水返歸<br />\n<br />\n最仆街係話聽日係和理非回合，勇武就係鬼<br />\n<br />\n雖然程度可能唔同，但和理非同勇武做嘅都係增加港共管治成本，施加最大壓力，如果係咁點解一定只可以和理非先？<br />\n<br />\n兩個幾月黎勇武手足都唔會搞到和理非遊行，佢地都係和理非集會地點之外或者之後行動，真心唔明點解要限死邊一日就一定要點，唔可以靈活變通？<br />\n<br />\n最後d捉鬼撚收皮啦，鬼未搞散行動就俾俾你地先自我解散呀"},{"pid":"c7550dfb5c4165b055966436476aff928b5a16db","tid":1480092,"uid":20283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:10:34.000Z","msg":"[置頂] 818要人呀 幫手推<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1479238\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1479238</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6475576b0ed9d1b62e86d74e3487690e1463fba2","tid":1480092,"uid":14153,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:12:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">真正和理非唔勇武但好勇敢，我親眼見嘅</span></span>"},{"pid":"b8777231be438bafbef165d56c28e5701035eb6f","tid":1480092,"uid":14153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:15:13.000Z","msg":"風向撚退散<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31ab4ac116fdb9204ef9692f91e069bf9b77615b","tid":1480092,"uid":147217,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T07:19:09.000Z","msg":"勇武手足唔係冇腦 連佢地都知聽日要和理非 你就係個風向撚"},{"pid":"4d1fb76e2bbc46b4b66c2d6146fc9c9f0f082f6c","tid":1480092,"uid":14153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31ab4ac116fdb9204ef9692f91e069bf9b77615b","tid":1480092,"uid":147217,"like":3,"di